Classes:
Name
Description
InputProcessing
Raw BioChip signal data (Amper/sec) is acquired from the transducer card and initially messaged before being transformed by the Data Transformation component.
DataTransformation
Biochip signal data is converted to the result using an algorithm. Each assay type has its own algorithm for the calculation.
OutputProcessing
The calculated result is converted to the test result to display as "sepsis positive" or "sepsis negative".
DataValidation
Data is monitored to observe if they are in the correct range.
ProtectedOnesComp
The data is stored twice - once in normal form and once in one's complement form.
ProtectedCRC
A cyclic redundancy check over data attribute values to identify in vivo corruption.
